* Merge pull request #4 from secc/feature-gm-ROCK8640-ConnectGate-v3

SECC Connect Button Visibility Gate

* ROCK-8867 Enforce S&S connect gate server-side on all connect paths

Gate was enforced on button visibility only; the board card-menu
postback, board modal handler, and detail Connect handler could all
still connect gated requests. Guard all three server-side and extract
the duplicated gate logic into App_Code/SeccConnectGateHelper so the
two blocks cannot drift.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>

